 177:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //! @brief      Clock prescaler enumeration.
 178:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //! @details    Clock prescaler options associated with TIMER0.
 179:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //! @warning    The value associate with the symbolic names may change
 180:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //!                 between builds and might not reflect the register/bits
 181:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //!                 real values. In order to ensure compatibility between
 182:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //!                 builds, always refer to the SYMBOLIC NAME, instead of
 183:funsape/peripheral/timer0.hpp ****     //!                 its VALUE.
